just because you want them.

115
00:10:08,874 --> 00:10:10,576
Some people just fall out of love

116
00:10:10,576 --> 00:10:11,978
out of nowhere.

117
00:10:11,978 --> 00:10:15,982
Some people just fail the tests out of nowhere.

118
00:10:15,982 --> 00:10:17,483
I'm doomed.

119
00:10:17,483 --> 00:10:18,951
It's over.

120
00:10:18,951 --> 00:10:20,286
Let's go.

121
00:10:30,730 --> 00:10:31,864
Come in.

122
00:10:39,252 --> 00:10:40,160
[NO.9]

123
00:10:43,275 --> 00:10:44,744
What's wrong?

124
00:10:44,744 --> 00:10:46,812
Number 9 isn't having problems again, is it?

125
00:10:48,247 --> 00:10:50,316
Will an artificial intelligence like Heng 9,

126
00:10:50,316 --> 00:10:51,648
officially go on the market in the future?

127
00:10:52,652 --> 00:10:54,353
Can its appearance age?

128
00:10:58,024 --> 00:10:59,659
But to me,

129
00:10:59,659 --> 00:11:01,427
you're more than just a commodity.

130
00:11:01,427 --> 00:11:04,397
You are unique and irreplaceable.

131
00:11:07,233 --> 00:11:10,069
It's not like you're marrying an AI,
so what's there to worry about?

132
00:11:10,069 --> 00:11:12,271
I want him to have no worries.

133
00:11:13,305 --> 00:11:14,707
What do you mean?

134
00:11:14,707 --> 00:11:17,877
I want to be with him like normal people are.

135
00:11:17,877 --> 00:11:19,178
Normal people?

136
00:11:19,178 --> 00:11:21,113
But he's not human.

137
00:11:21,113 --> 00:11:22,214
Chu Yiping.

138
00:11:22,214 --> 00:11:23,683
I sent him to you as a caretaker,

139
00:11:23,683 --> 00:11:24,984
not to fall in love with you.

140
00:11:24,984 --> 00:11:26,752
What are you doing?

141
00:11:28,921 --> 00:11:31,490
But to me, he is Heng 9.

142
00:11:31,490 --> 00:11:32,758
He exists for me,

143
00:11:32,758 --> 00:11:34,760
and everything about him revolves around me.

144
00:11:35,728 --> 00:11:37,563
He gives me a sense of companionship
that I've never had before,

145
00:11:37,563 --> 00:11:39,799
so I want to be with him for a lifetime.

146
00:11:42,001 --> 00:11:43,102
A lifetime?

147
00:11:45,371 --> 00:11:46,839
You've never fallen in love with a person.

148
00:11:46,839 --> 00:11:48,240
What makes you think that way?

149
00:11:49,475 --> 00:11:53,512
Look, you say he exists for you.

150
00:11:54,814 --> 00:11:57,116
But I'm telling you now.

151
00:11:57,116 --> 00:11:59,652
He exists for the user,

152
00:11:59,652 --> 00:12:03,222
and that user just happens to be you.

153
00:12:04,023 --> 00:12:06,092
Everything he does for you

154
00:12:06,092 --> 00:12:08,094
is all pre-programmed,

155
00:12:09,095 --> 00:12:10,563
and the one you should fall in love with

156
00:12:12,531 --> 00:12:15,234
is the engineer who inputs data into him,

157
00:12:15,234 --> 00:12:17,837
not the AI that is programmed.

158
00:12:17,837 --> 00:12:19,138
Do you understand?

159
00:12:23,909 --> 00:12:26,846
And now, No. 9 wants to leave you

160
00:12:26,846 --> 00:12:28,848
because you're boring, right?

161
00:12:32,485 --> 00:12:34,153
Did he tell you that?

162
00:12:35,488 --> 00:12:36,889
That he wants to leave?

163
00:12:45,731 --> 00:12:47,500
Yiping.

164
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:49,802
You've just been alone for too long.

165
00:12:49,802 --> 00:12:51,403
This is pure projection.

166
00:12:53,139 --> 00:12:55,007
Besides,

167
00:12:55,007 --> 00:12:56,475
