168
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,948
You are No. 9's first owner.

169
00:13:04,316 --> 00:13:06,318
After his mission is completed,

170
00:13:06,886 --> 00:13:08,854
he will be sent back to the factory

171
00:13:08,854 --> 00:13:10,856
for maintenance and RESET,

172
00:13:12,658 --> 00:13:14,960
preparing to serve the next owner.

173
00:13:16,962 --> 00:13:18,531
No. 9 wants to leave already.

174
00:13:19,932 --> 00:13:21,967
So don't get lost in it, okay?

175
00:14:18,711 --> 00:14:25,855
♫ Turns out that a long time is not forever ♫

176
00:14:25,855 --> 00:14:28,447
♫ A hand held for so long ♫

177
00:14:28,447 --> 00:14:32,489
♫ Has become a hand waving goodbye ♫

178
00:14:32,489 --> 00:14:37,663
♫ The promises so bravely
voiced at the beginning ♫

179
00:14:37,663 --> 00:14:41,600
♫ Have now lost the reason to be fulfilled ♫

180
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:47,237
♫ Perhaps nowhere would be ♫

181
00:14:47,800 --> 00:14:50,864
♫ The best destination for us ♫

182
00:15:07,032 --> 00:15:09,376
♫ No one has changed ♫

183
00:15:10,814 --> 00:15:13,408
♫ There's no need to speculate ♫

184
00:15:14,712 --> 00:15:17,088
♫ On the contrary ♫

185
00:15:17,816 --> 00:15:21,632
♫ Our ending has nothing to do
with not loving anymore ♫

186
00:15:23,589 --> 00:15:26,258
The reason that made me
rush back recklessly that day

187
00:15:26,258 --> 00:15:29,824
♫ The story may take a new twist ♫

188
